ng></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#15803d;line-height:1.5\">Recibirás una invitación de Google Calendar con un enlace de <strong>Google Meet</strong> para tu reunión virtual. Acéptala para que aparezca en tu calendario.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:24px\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase\">🔖 Resumen de tu consulta</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.6\">{{$node[\"Parsear JSON\"].json.motivo_consulta}}</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:24px\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600\">Modalidad</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;font-size:14px;color:#1e293b\">Virtual (Google Meet)</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600\">Duración</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;font-size:14px;color:#1e293b\">2 horas</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 16px;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600\">Categoría</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 16px;font-size:14px;color:#1e293b\">{{$node[\"Parsear JSON\"].json.categoria_servicio}}</td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:24px\">\n      <a href=\"https://r3consultores.com\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#f6b034;color:#1e293b;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px\">Visitar r3consultores.com</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;margin:0\">Si necesitas reagendar o cancelar, responde a este correo o contáctanos por WhatsApp al <strong>+57 300 4046628</strong>.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#1e293b;padding:20px 40px;text-align:center\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:11px;color:#f6b034;font-weight:600\">R3 CONSULTORES S.A.S.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8\">Asesoría Contable, Legal y Financiera</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:10px;color:#475569\">info@r3consultores.com · +57 300 4046628 · r3consultores.com</p>\n  </div>\n</div>",
